—维拉谈创作犯罪游戏<ref name="10 Years" />}}

游戏的执法人员非常严苛。玩家违法行为按性质分“轻微”和“严重”。玩家轻微违法（如超速或闯红灯）会被罚款（自由模式为1000美元，主线模式无金额），严重违法（如斗殴或拿出武器）会被直接逮捕或开枪击毙。连续四次轻微犯罪等同于严重犯罪。警力随玩家违反严重性而增加，甚至动用路钉或从玩家车后开枪扫射。

== 开发 ==
游戏开发从1998年末开始，代号“Gangster”，原打算做成类似于《{{le|车手 (游戏)|Driver (video game)|车手}}》的赛车游戏。原本计划加入的多人游戏模式和赛车模式没有出现在游戏最终版本中。发售时间定在2000年。之前用于《{{le|危机最前线|Hidden & Dangerous}}》的引擎由于无法满足开发者的需求，于是本作改用LS3D引擎。更换引擎导致游戏发行比原计划晚两年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.databaze-her.cz/hry/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven/zajimavosti/ |title=Czech |publisher=Databaze-her.cz |accessdate=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2014-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140820002243/http://www.databaze-her.cz/hry/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven/zajimavosti/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Mondschein, Pavel |url=http://bonusweb.idnes.cz/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven-preview-dsn-/Preview.aspx?c=A011106_mafiap_bw |title=Czech |publisher=Bonusweb.idnes.cz |accessdate=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304132945/http://bonusweb.idnes.cz/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven-preview-dsn-/Preview.aspx?c=A011106_mafiap_bw |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Martin Šebela (hadl) |url=http://mafia.gamecentral.cz/mafia-informace/vyvoj |title=Czech |publisher=Mafia.gamecentral.cz |accessdate=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2014-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626055904/http://mafia.gamecentral.cz/mafia-informace/vyvoj |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2004年，游戏移植到[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]和[[Xbox|Xbox]]平台。Illusion没有参加游戏移植。自由驾驶模式中警察巡逻、真实性和画面细节等PC版特色在主机版没有体现。游戏其实受《[[好家伙|-{zh-hans:好家伙;zh-hk:盜亦有道;zh-tw:四海好傢伙;}-]]》和《[[教父_(电影)|教父]]》等影片灵感启发，基调定得更加严肃和成熟。导演丹尼尔·维拉希望打造一台丰富的戏剧，加入戏剧、动作和幽默，增强游戏现实感<ref>Smith, Edward. [http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/mafia-director-daniel-vavra-gta-grand-theft-409859 ''10 Years On: Interview With Mafia Director Daniel Vavra''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/mafia-director-daniel-vavra-gta-grand-theft-409859 |date=20180628015639 }}, ibtimes.co.uk 29 November 2012. Retrieved on 5 October 2015.</ref>。

游戏2012年在[[蒸汽|Steam]]下架后，于2017年在[[GOG.com|GOG.com]]重新发行了免[[数字版权管理|数字版权管理]]版。GOG版完全保留了原版的内容，但因版权问题删掉配乐<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven-comes-to-gog-years-after-vanishing-from-steam/|title=Mafia: The City of Lost Heaven comes to GOG, years after vanishing from Steam|last=Roberts|first=Samuel|date=2017-10-19|work=PC Gamer|accessdate=2017-10-20|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003229/https://www.pcgamer.com/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven-comes-to-gog-years-after-vanishing-from-steam/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.neowin.net/news/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven-is-purchasable-once-again-after-five-years|title=Mafia: The City of Lost Heaven is purchasable once again after five years - Neowin|last=Ariyasinghe|first=Pulasthi|date=2017-10-19|work=Neowin|accessdate=2017-10-20|archive-date=2019-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914143630/https://www.neowin.net/news/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven-is-purchasable-once-again-after-five-years|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-10-19-the-original-mafia-is-back-from-digital-purgatory-and-out-on-gog|title=The original Mafia is back from digital purgatory and out on GOG|last=Wales|first=Matt|date=2017-10-19|work=Eurogamer|accessdate=2017-10-20|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809224458/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-10-19-the-original-mafia-is-back-from-digital-purgatory-and-out-on-gog|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

