游戏发行后，评论家和玩家们便认为本作比一般的《侠盗猎车手》风格游戏更写实，更严谨。游戏的城市面积比当时大多数游戏都大，设有多种开放的交通工具，并增加广阔的郊野地带。[[IGN|IGN]]的丹·亚当斯（{{lang|en|Dan Adams}}）给游戏打出9.2分（满分10分）<ref name="Mafiapcrev-IGN"/>，同时[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]称PC版是“年度最佳游戏之一”，并打出9.3分（满分10分）<ref name="Mafiapcrev-Gamespot"/>。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》认为本作优于《[[侠盗猎车手III|侠盗猎车手III]]》，写道：“从你居住的城市，到难以置信地写实的载具，这作品有着直击心肠的重磅炸弹<ref name=gi/>。”

虽然最初的PC版获得广泛的赞誉，但PlayStation 2和Xbox版，在许多评论家看来较差，便打出较低的分数<ref name="GSpotPS2"/><ref name="GSpotXB"/><ref name="IGNPS2"/><ref name="IGNXB"/><ref>{{cite web |author=Matt Keller |url=http://palgn.com.au/playstation-2/1014/mafia-review/ |title=Mafia Review - PlayStation 2 Video Game Review |publisher=PALGN |date=2004-02-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009104710/http://palgn.com.au/playstation-2/1014/mafia-review/ |archivedate=2012-10-09 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-09-12 }}</ref>。在游戏开发商所在国家[[捷克|捷克]]，游戏获得评论家和玩家们的普通赞赏，甚至在捷克调查机构BonusWeb的调查中被选为最优秀的捷克和斯洛伐克开发游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hodnoceniher.cz/pc/akcni/mafia.html |title=Czech |publisher=Hodnoceniher.cz |date= |accessdate=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2013-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130915114239/http://www.hodnoceniher.cz/pc/akcni/mafia.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.databaze-her.cz/hry/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven/ |title=Czech |publisher=Databaze-her.cz |date= |accessdate=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2014-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419124328/http://www.databaze-her.cz/hry/mafia-the-city-of-lost-heaven/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]]表示，截至2008年3月12日，游戏共售出200万份<ref>{{cite web |author=Matt Martin |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/grand-theft-auto-series-has-sold-66-million-units-to-date |title=Grand Theft Auto series has sold 66 million units to date |publisher=GamesIndustry.biz |date=2008-03-12 |accessdate=2008-04-01 |archive-date=2017-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813083449/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/grand-theft-auto-series-has-sold-66-million-units-to-date |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://taketwovalue.com/documents/TTWO_Value.pdf#page=9 |title=Industry-Leading IP Portfolio: 15 Million Unit Plus Owned Franchises |publisher=Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc. |date=2008-03-26 |page=9 |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080408234728/http://taketwovalue.com/documents/TTWO_Value.pdf#page=9 |archivedate=2008-04-08 |accessdate=2008-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=survey>{{cite web |url=http://bonusweb.idnes.cz/nejlepsi-cesko-slovenska-hra-vyhlaseni-ankety-fqo-/Magazin.aspx?c=A141203_154335_bw-magazin_anb |title=Nejlepší česko-slovenská hra? Že neuhádnete, kdo na plné čáře vyhrál |publisher=Bonusweb |accessdate=2014-12-04 |archive-date=2014-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210105044/http://bonusweb.idnes.cz/nejlepsi-cesko-slovenska-hra-vyhlaseni-ankety-fqo-/Magazin.aspx?c=A141203_154335_bw-magazin_anb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

