==黑手党：终极版==
{{main|黑手党：终极版}}
2020年5月13日，[[2K_Games|2K Games]]公布《黑手党：失落天堂》的网站重制版<ref>{{Cite web|title=Live the life of a gangster across three distinct eras of organized crime in America. Discover the #MafiaTrilogy Tuesday, May 19 at 9am PT / 12pm ET / 5pm BST at MafiaGame.com|url=https://twitter.com/mafiagame/status/1260570564844040194?s=20|last=Trilogy|first=Mafia:|date=2020-05-13|website=@mafiagame|language=en|access-date=2020-05-16|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918081206/https://twitter.com/mafiagame/status/1260570564844040194?s=20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，定名《黑手党：终极版》。重制版将列入到2020年已发布的三部《黑手党》作品的收藏系列《黑手党：三部曲》，该系列由[[Hangar_13|Hangar 13]]开发。与[[數位修復|數位修復]]版的《[[黑手党II|黑手党II]]》和获大量更新的《[[黑手党III|黑手党III]]》不同，《终极版》为完全重建，扩展了原版的剧情，完全更改了失落天堂的风景，对游戏玩法进行大修并引入了摩托车，还有全新的“原创配乐”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mafia Trilogy announcement coming on May 19|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/mafia-trilogy-announcement-coming-on-may-19/|last=Brown|first=Fraser|date=2020-05-13|website=PC Gamer|language=en-US|access-date=2020-05-16|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521231701/https://www.pcgamer.com/mafia-trilogy-announcement-coming-on-may-19/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Mafia series is getting a trilogy re-release|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-05-13-the-mafia-series-is-getting-a-trilogy-re-release|last=Phillips|first=Tom|date=2020-05-13|website=Eurogamer|language=en|access-date=2020-05-16|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516221638/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-05-13-the-mafia-series-is-getting-a-trilogy-re-release|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mafia: Definitive Edition leaks via store page, and it’s a full remake – not a remaster|url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/mafia/definitive-edition-release-date|last=Bailey|first=Dustin|date=2020-05-13|website={{tsl|en|PCGamesN||PCGamesN}}|language=en|access-date=2020-05-17|archive-date=2020-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522020356/https://www.pcgamesn.com/mafia/definitive-edition-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏于2020年9月25日在[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]发行<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mafia Remake Is A 'Complete Overhaul' Of The Original Game|url=https://kotaku.com/mafia-remake-is-a-complete-overhaul-of-the-original-gam-1843544095|last=Gach|first=Ethan|date=2020-05-19|website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|language=en|access-date=2020-05-24|archive-date=2020-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520143629/https://kotaku.com/mafia-remake-is-a-complete-overhaul-of-the-original-gam-1843544095|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Chalk|first=Andy|date=2020-07-07|title=Mafia: Definitive Edition has been delayed|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/mafia-definitive-edition-has-been-delayed/|access-date=2020-07-08|website=PC Gamer|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920120038/https://www.pcgamer.com/mafia-definitive-edition-has-been-delayed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

